data.description: Charm, location and the price is RIGHT! Best curb appeal in the area and priced to sell AS-IS. Full Roof replacement Aug '23, Full HVAC '21, Water Heater '23, TuffShed on concrete slab '22, Gas range  dishwasher '19, Both showers remodeled '23 and the Washer  Dryer '22 and kitchen refrigerator are available too. Conveniently located between Hwy 183 and 183A, just minutes from 1890 Ranch, The HEB Center, Whole Foods and the highly acclaimed Leander ISD schools!
